{
  "stem": "1061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, because-- Anyhow, so these were people of another-- they were-- they were peasant type, but very decent people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there was a little boy, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I played with him in the snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But mother helped her give birth to the child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And believe me, she must have just walked out of the barn where she cleaned the horses and fed them, and went and had the baby.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That's-- that's exactly how it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Anyhow, it was from that last apartment with the-- where we lived with the teamsters that the final solution came in our hometown.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So that was our last residence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father then was given some kind of a job in a-- as a scribe, you know, because he-- he was very literate.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a scribe somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this-- those were very difficult times, very.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because right way, as I mentioned before, we were cut off from everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the children were cut off from school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the men were cut off from their livelihood, especially a man of my father's position.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, storekeepers still had stores and such, but our existence changed completely, totally.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, in the ghetto, there were stores where-- there were-- food-- food was rationed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was constant fear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was constant fear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And still there-- there was, with all this fear and with all the uncertainty, and with all the anticipation of something horrible to come, there was the life, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was, as I told you, the classes that were conducted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I do remember there was a very transport of people from Lodz sent to our hometown.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And soon enough, my sisters found friends among them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were budding poets or whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I still remember hearing Lord Byron's poetry read in Polish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they had these-- these evenings, these literary evenings, and there was a semblance of normal life, though-- even though it really wasn't normal, the make believe made it so, because still there was this exchange of-- of ideas, of-- of culture, you see.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as long as we were still at home, meaning whichever home it was, whether it was the first or the last, there was this semblance.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "For example, I remember my mother made a-- my-- Regina was engaged and Mother made the party for her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she put little pieces so fern on the table cloth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she made it pretty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, those things counted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Those were the things that really uplifted you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And of course, unfortunately, from that last apartment is where we-- everything changed after that.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
